OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fplenty of sunny spells through the
OL,7,Fevening. Staying dry overnight with
OL,8,Flong clear spells developing. Mild,
OL,9,Fvery mild in places, with light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FBecoming warm or very warm on
OL,12,FFriday with plenty of sunshine,
OL,13,Falthough this may turn hazy at times.
OL,14,FMild overnight with patchy cloud and a
OL,15,Frisk of isolated showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
